sunkit-image
============

|Latest Version| |codecov| |Powered by NumFOCUS| |Powered by Sunpy|

.. |Powered by Sunpy| image:: http://img.shields.io/badge/powered%20by-SunPy-orange.svg?style=flat
   :target: https://www.sunpy.org
